name: My Résumé
body:
My Résumé in LaTeX format
=========================

This is a page for my Github repository hosting the original source `.tex` and the accompanying 
font and image files.

I have also provided a PDF version, for easy download, exported from the source files.  
I used the service [WriteLatex](https://www.writelatex.com/read/ywcsbdngvhmb) for the PDF conversion.
     
One of the great features of the `.tex` file,  it can be [converted](http://tex.stackexchange.com/questions/3/compiling-documents-online) to almost any file type, including [RTF](http://www.sciweavers.org/convert-latex-to-rtf).

Please feel free to download my résumé and distribute it as much as you like.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
